OL,3,CHuge mound of waste dumped on public
OL,4,Cbridleway
OL,6,FA huge mound of waste has been dumped
OL,7,Fon a public bridleway in
OL,8,FWorcestershire.
OL,10,FThe pile near Evesham started around
OL,11,Ftwo months ago, and has been growing
OL,12,Fsince.
OL,14,FMountains of dumped rubbish are being
OL,15,Finvestigated at suspected illegal
OL,16,Fwaste sites in Worcestershire.
OL,18,FOne is a mass of rubbish dumped in a
OL,19,Flarge trench on Haselor Lane, Evesham,
OL,20,Fbeing investigated by Wychavon
OL,21,FDistrict Council.
