OL,3,CHuge mound of waste dumped on public
OL,4,Cbridleway
OL,6,FOne of the residents walking in the
OL,7,Farea said, "It used to be amazing,
OL,8,Fwalk your dogs, there's a bridleway,
OL,9,Fand you could walk right to Evesham. I
OL,10,Fwalked past there the first morning,
OL,11,Fand the smell was disgusting. Steam
OL,12,Fwas coming out of it. You could see
OL,13,Fsomething was wrong. It wasn't normal."
OL,15,F"I can't walk them (my dogs) down
OL,16,Fthere anymore. If you have a puppy,
OL,17,Fthey ruffle through it, and the next
OL,18,Fthing you know, they come past you
OL,19,Fwith some sort of object in their
OL,20,Fmouth you don't want to see to be
OL,21,Fhonest. It's disgusting."
