OL,6,FFurther complaints centre on Stone
OL,7,FArrow Farm in the village of
OL,8,FPeopleton, which the Environment
OL,9,FAgency is reported to have said had
OL,10,Fseen "illegal waste-dumping activity."
OL,12,FAn Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid, "Illegal waste crime scars our
OL,14,Fcommunities and the site in Peopleton
OL,15,Fis something we're committed to
OL,16,Ftackling together with West Mercia
OL,17,FPolice, Worcestershire County Council
OL,18,Fand Wychavon District Council.
