OL,6,F"Together we're pulling every lever
OL,7,Favailable to us to disrupt those who
OL,8,Fprofit from the harm illegal waste
OL,9,Fsites cause."
OL,11,FA spokesman for Wychavon District
OL,12,FCouncil said, "We are aware of
OL,13,Fpotential illegal waste activity at
OL,14,Fthis site. As our powers are limited
OL,15,Fto deal with this sort of crime, we
OL,16,Fare working proactively with partners,
OL,17,Fincluding the Environment Agency, to
OL,18,Faddress any potential issues at
OL,19,FHaselor Lane, as well as deal with
OL,20,Fwaste crime across our district.
